data.text:
Music Box features a diverse array of nationally celebrated talent, local legends, and up-and-coming acts. Founded in the tradition of legendary venues such as San Francisco’s Fillmore, and LA’s Palladium, El Rey, and Wiltern, we are truly unique among San Diego nightlife destinations. Seeing a show at Music Box is a concertgoer’s dream! With a 700+ capacity, our venue is large enough for a full concert experience, yet cozy enough to feel like you’re at an intimate show with your favorite band.

Amplify your experience at Music Box San Diego by reserving the best seats in the house! With three levels of concert viewing and food and beverage options for any group size, we have everything you need for a night to remember. To book your VIP Table and Bottle Service at our next show, contact Krag at (619) 836-1847 or vip@musicboxsd.com.
